          }
        },
        "text_kCdfmD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>At TABASQUISHY®, we believe every feeling deserves a soft landing.</strong></p><p>Born from a heartfelt moment between a mother and child, TABASQUISHY™ has grown into a global community — but our mission remains the same: <em>to create soft spaces in a hard world.</em></p><p><strong>To celebrate our anniversary, here’s something truly special:</strong></p><p><strong>🐨 Exclusive limited-time price on iconic IP squishies</strong></p><p><strong>📅 Aug 20 – Sep 20 only</strong></p><p>🔒 <strong>Limit: Up to 2 IP squishies per customer at $5.99 each (original price $15.99). Additional pieces will be charged at full price</strong></p><p>🎁 <strong>Stacks with “Buy 3, Get 1 Free” for even more softness</strong></p><p>It’s our way of saying <em>thank you</em> for every pause, every smile, every soft moment you’ve shared with us.</p><p>We’re here to remind the world:</p><p>You don’t need to be fixed. You just need a squishy. ❤️</p>",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        }
      },
